{"id":569227,"date":[{"year":1978,"month":6,"day":20}],"page":"2","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"126","ytitle":"","mtitle":"郭老逝世敬制小诗以志哀思","ftitle":"","authors":["端木蕻良"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"端木蕻良"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蜀水朱龙飞向天【注】，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于今破壁四十年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心逐梅花香到骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手植新竹绿满川。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陵江投尽思公黍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长峡泪没屈子船。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“星空”夜望星千斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是“女神”眼中焆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"【注】在雾都重庆与友人看望郭老时，室内垟上悬有刚出土的朱拓飞龙，故云。"}]}